      • type

        private int type
        product type.
        • com.konakartadmin.bl.KonakartAdminConstants.PHYSICAL_PROD_TYPE = physical product
        • com.konakartadmin.bl.KonakartAdminConstants.DIGITAL_DOWNLOAD_PROD_TYPE = digital download product
        • com.konakartadmin.bl.KonakartAdminConstants.FREE_SHIPPING_PROD_TYPE = physical product with free shipping
        • com.konakartadmin.bl.KonakartAdminConstants.BUNDLE_PROD_TYPE = a product that bundles other product
        • com.konakartadmin.bl.KonakartAdminConstants.FREE_SHIPPING_BUNDLE_PROD_TYPE = a product that bundles other product with free shipping
        • com.konakartadmin.bl.KonakartAdminConstants.GIFT_CERTIFICATE_PRODUCT_TYPE = a gift certificate product
        • com.konakartadmin.bl.ProductMgr.BOOKABLE_PRODUCT_TYPE = a product that has a schedule and can have bookings (i.e. a training course)
        • com.konakartadmin.bl.ProductMgr.VIRTUAL_PRODUCT_TYPE = a virtual product such as a service, warranty or donation
